(6, 'SOMA', '{\"p1\":\" Since Vedic times, Soma has been an important god. However the Vedas have dwelt more on his plant like than human form. He has been projected as a very attractive god and Indra, Agni, Varuna, Mitra are all keen to acquire Soma. He has been defined as the wealth of the Gods, best of medicinal herbs, the King of the Plant Kingdom and therefore has been assigned the status of a God. Soma is also synonymous with the Moon.\",\"p2\":\"When Soma is assigned the northernmost pada in the Vaastu chakra, then he becomes one of the ashtavasus. Soma had a son called Varcha meaning fame and wealth. Samrangan Sutradhar associates Soma with Kubera. If a door is located in this pada, then the inhabitants attain all qualities and wealth.\"}', 'ॐवयं सोमव्रतेतवमनस्तनूषुबिभ्रतः। प्रजावन्तः सचेमहि ॐभू भो: सोमइहा ॐसोमायनमः।।', 'assets/devtas/Soma N5.jpg', '{\"1\":\"Power to earn profits and safeguard it.\",\"2\":\"The drink of immortality, the essence\",\"3\":\"Possesses magical properties.\",\"4\":\"Associated with Moon, lord of subconscious mind and Kuber, lord of wealth.\",\"5\":\"It\'s associated with right brain, subtle thoughts.\",\"6\":\"What to do with money, how to manage it, invest it comes from Soma.\",\"7\":\"Flow of money happens with a good combined balancing with Soma and Bhallat.\",\"8\":\"Entrance here makes fire weak and thus makes a person like to live a life full of satisfaction/ gives a religious bent of mind. Because of Chandra, it makes you satisfied/ Good progeny, overall bliss and wealth.\",\"9\":\"Manipur Chakra--Fire element--power of transformation:\",\"10\":\"He is the lord of Speech also called \'Vachaspati\'\",\"11\":\"Soma has the power of giving luck and fortune (Saubhagya) to females.\",\"12\":\"Soma gives strength to earn profits in business and safety from the enemies.\",\"13\":\"He creates such a magic in whatever you do that it attracts the attention of other person standing before you.\",\"14\":\"Soma has the power which practically converts your work into money.\",\"15\":\"If Soma is balanced, you will immediately get the people who will appreciate your efforts and purchase your product and services.\"}', '{\"name\":\"SOMA (N5)\",\"color\":\"Red\",\"direction\":\"North \",\"C1\":\"Transformation/Treasure \",\"C2\":\" Pranamaya Kosha\",\"C3\":\"Left Shoulder/Banya Kandha \",\"C4\":\"Manipur/Alpha\",\"C5\":\"Panna\"}'),
(7, 'Diti', '{\"p1\":\"Of the 13 wives of Prajapati Kashyapa, Diti was one of them. This name has appeared thrice in the Rig Veda, twice with Aditi. Aditi was the mother of the Gods and Diti was the mother of the demons. Inspite of her demonic nature, Diti has godly qualities inhibited within her. Their children were jealous of each other and always fighting. Diti\'s sons grew upto be called the Daityas. Hiranyakashyap and Hiranyaksha were her two sons, who were killed by the Gods. Diti then prayed to Kashyap for a son who could defeat the Gods. She was granted a boon by the sage and gave birth to the 49 Marudgana sons, who became Lord Indra\'s helpers and thus received the Devyoni.\",\"p2\":\"Diti has been assigned the pada in the North east corner of the vaastu chakra.\"}', 'ॐ अदितिौरदितिरन्तरिक्षमदितिर्मातासपितासपुत्रः। विश्वेदेवा अदितिः पंचजनाऽअदितिर्जातमदितिर्जनित्वम्।  ॐ भू भोदिते इहा ॐओंदितये नमः।।', 'assets/devtas/Diti N8.jpg', '{\"1\":\"Broad mind , Far-sightedness, freedom of thought\",\"2\":\"As it is sahastrar, delta wave, if imbalance It impacts to the very deep level \",\"3\":\"Removes all duality if balanced, total clarity\",\"4\":\"When balanced, it discourages sheep like following; you do not follow the traditions blindly. You have an individual personality. You would be able to know what to do and what not to do.\",\"5\":\"Power to say NO comes from this field\",\"6\":\"Imbalance here takes away clarity of mind; this power leads to confused mind. Person finds himself unable to visualize all the related aspects of a subject or situation and reach a decision.\",\"7\":\"Gives spirituality if entrance here and female dominance with important roles in life/ gives higher bank balance/poverty, stress, ailments and impediments\",\"8\":\"It cut, people loses courage to say NO.\"}', '{\"name\":\"DITI (N8)\",\"color\":\"Green\",\"direction\":\"NE\",\"C1\":\"Foresightedness/Visionary\",\"C2\":\"Anandmaya Kosh\",\"C3\":\"Left eye/Banyi Netra\",\"C4\":\"Sahasrar