(35, 'GRIHAKSHAT', '{\"p1\":\"Grihashat is actually one of the Vishwadevas and is installed as a group of 10 gods or 33 gods if we go by the Rig Veda. These gods prevent a house from getting disintegrated and act for the welfare of man. They protect us and organize the cycle of happiness and sorrow in life. If these Gods are happy, they keep the house united and if they are unhappy they fragment the household. Their mother was Vishwa, wife of Dharma.\"}', 'सवितात्वासनां सुवतामग्निर्गृहपतीनां सोमोवनस्पतीनाम्। बृहस्पतिर्वाचऽइन्द्रोज्यैष्ठ्यायरुद्र: पशुभ्यो मित्रः सत्योवरुणोधर्मपतीनाम्। ॐ भूर्भुवः स्वः भोगृहक्षतइहा ।। ॐ गृहक्षतायनमः।।', 'assets/devtas/Grihashat  Grihaspatya S4.jpg', '{\"1\":\"Gruha mean Mann and Akshat means Dayra ( Mann ka dayara)\",\"2\":\"Helps in self control\",\"3\":\"This is very important to achieve success in all desires.\",\"4\":\"Mercury energy field here\",\"5\":\"Defines the boundary of mind.\",\"6\":\"When imbalance, people forget their responsibilities and become relaxed and casual attitude.\",\"7\":\"Door is great here, gives birth of male child, productive output, Resident enjoy the life.\",\"8\":\"Blue colour and water can cause court case or misunderstanding.\",\"9\":\"Cause conflicts and commitment failure. Gives bad company of friends also\",\"10\":\"Big water body here causes indiscipline students.\",\"11\":\"Lack of peace if imbalanced\",\"12\":\"Children will be better disciplined if they sleep here and good behaviour.\",\"13\":\"If imbalanced, people will not listen to others, causes misunderstanding through words, makes us unable to relax.\"}', '{\"name\":\"GRIHAKSHAT  (S4)\",\"color\":\"Green\",\"direction\":\"south\",\"C1\":\"Limitation/Definer\",\"C2\":\"Manomaya Kosha\",\"C3\":\"Right Back/Dahina Pasharva\",\"C4\":\"Vishuddhi/Alpha\",\"C5\":\"Moonga\"}'),
(36, 'GANDHARVA', '{\"p1\":\"Gandharva is a group of gods described in the Vaastu mandala and the Sarvotobhadra mandala. Ten gandharvas were born of the union of Prajapati Kashyap and Pradha, daughter of Daksha. Some other Gandharvas were born off Arishtha and Kashyap according to Matsya Purana.\",\"p2\":\"These are divine Gandharvas who look after the welfare of their devotees and grant them intellect. They perform their duties and are skilled at dancing, singing and reciting songs of praise. They impart these skills to their disciples, Narada being one of them.\",\"p3\":\"Gandharva occupies the pada next to Yama in the South and those who are desirous of mastering these skills should appease this lord and practice regularly.\"}', 'ॐप्रतद्दोचेदमृतंनुविद्दान्गन्धर्वो धमबिभृतंगुहासत्। त्रीणिपदानिनिहितागुहास्य यस्तानिवेदसपितुः पितासत्। ॐ भूर्भुवः स्वः भोगंधर्वइहा गंधर्वाय नमः।।', 'assets/devtas/Gandharva S6.jpg', '{\"1\":\"People good in music are called Gandharv\",\"2\":\"Balanced here gives relaxation , happiness, vacations\",\"3\":\"If area is cut, people will not get vacations for a long time\",\"4\":\"If extended and living room here, people are in party mood and don’t take anything seriously.\",\"5\":\"Ladies Sleeping here regularly, have complained of having dirty thoughts\",\"6\":\"If kitchen here , people want varieties in food.\",\"7\":\"Dining table will cause excess expenditure of food items.\",\"8\":\"TV, Musical systems, books are  source of recreation here.\",\"9\":\"Alcohol can be kept here\",\"10\":\"If extended, people will be extra relaxed and if cut, people will be extra active.\",\"11\":\"Extend this area in Hotel business, discotheque or party hall.\",\"12\":\"Toilet here, people don\'t take break from work for years.\",\"13\":\"Gandharva has all the secrets of the sky and all the mystical powers from Satya. They also give the ecstatic states of mind.\",\"14\":\"They are considered the adheestha dev of music and all kinds of arts.\"}', '{\"name\"