(37, 'BHRINGRAJ', '{\"p1\":\"Bhringaraia is known as the Goddess of the black bees. She occupies the pada adjacent to the Gandharvas and symbolises the apsaras. Gandharvas and apsaras are nearly always placed together. A black bee represents love and apsaras also symbolize love. In the Vaastu chakra Bhringaraja is located on the right thigh of the Vaastu purush and this place promotes the gandharva vidyas.\"}', ' ॐ सुपर्णः पार्जन्य आर्तिर्वाहसोदर्विदाते वायवेबृहस्पतने वाचस्पये पैङ्गराजोऽलजः आन्तरिक्षप्लवोमद्गमत्स्यस्ते नदीपतयेद्यावापृथिवीयः कूर्मः। ॐ भूर्भुवः स्वः भोः शृंगराजइहा. शृंगराजायनमः।।', 'assets/devtas/Bhringaraja S7.jpg', '{\"1\":\"Imparts the discretion power of what they should keep or remove in life\",\"2\":\"Can keep cosmetic here\",\"3\":\"Helps in controlling abortion and miscarriage.\",\"4\":\"Gives the wisdom to assess things properly.\",\"5\":\"Toilet is excellent here, it facilitates balanced and smooth process of disposal at all the three levels of body--physical, energy, and mind.\",\"6\":\"All efforts are waste if bed here\",\"7\":\"If extended, gives more females child\",\"8\":\"It is advised to spend 20 minutes to let go of useless thoughts and things.\",\"9\":\"Entrance – total wastage of efforts.\",\"10\":\"If someone asks :kya kare ya na kare “, then check \",\"11\":\"Causes rigid mind if more time is spent here.\",\"12\":\"Sleeping here, all your efforts waste. Body part coming in the zone starts facing problem.\",\"13\":\"A pregnent lady sleeps here undergoes lots of problems.\",\"14\":\"Put alcohol bottle in this zone if want to leave alcohol.\",\"15\":\"if food storage here, spoiled very fast.\",\"16\":\"Dining table here gives digestion problem. \",\"17\":\"This field is the element of being genius., the power to grant wisdom and to manifest what is left after removing the unnecessary element.\",\"18\":\"When imbalanced, it leads to increase expenditure, efforts not becoming successful and the person wasting time and energy in useles